    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Utivarachna ichneumon Deeleman-Reinhold, 2001, male, holotype (RNMH.ARA.15223). A habitus, dorsal view; B same, ventral view; C cephalic part and chelicerae, frontal view; D leg I, left, prolateral view; E label. Scale bars: A–C, 1 mm; D, 0.50 mm." ;
