    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Utivarachna ichneumon, male, holotype (RNMH.ARA.15223). A left palp, prolateral view; B same, ventral view; C same, retrolateral view; D same, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.50 mm. E—embolus, Sd—sperm duct, St—subtegulum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8324308/files/figure.png" ;
